{
  "stem": "322.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I'll tell you, it's not that-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] you, you, you just couldn't live there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It just didn't make sense to even go there, because it reminded you of what was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you look.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It just isn't here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is not the same place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I look around, and I was used to seeing-- after all, Munkacs-- practically 50% of the population of Munkacs was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't see a Jewish child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I couldn't see-- I couldn't-- there were about, I'd say, out of, out of 16,000 Jews that left Munkacs, I don't think we were 200 altogether.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I decided to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I left with a, a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We heard that, that Bucharest is intact, and that some restitution will also be meted out, given to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we decided, two guys, you know, 18-year-olds, and went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we stayed there for about six weeks in Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we had, you might say, a, a, a sort of warming type-- you know, we were well-received by the, by the Jewish population there and well-fed by Zionist organizations.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- but I just had to go back again to Munkacs, and I stayed there until January of 1946.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was difficult to get out of there because, you know, the borders were beginning to close on us, and the communists were not, I must say, there they were not very friendly to anyone for that matter, very brutal.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians, the Red Army.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
